    Black Aracnia watched Megatron flee. It didnt matter now. THe battle was 
won, the ship saved, all thanks to her. As for the two intruders....they 
would be dead in minutes if not now. She watched Quickstrike scurry right 
into the corridor where Darkmouse was, which also was where the nerve gas was 
being let loose. He would stumble right into it. Fool.
    "Ah, being commander is good. Rampage will definetly owe me after this!"
